<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Account Deletion Confirmation</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333333;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .header {
        background-color: #e74c3c;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        color: white;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
      }

      .info-box {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }

      .footer {
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #888888;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
      }

      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: #3498db;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 4px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Account Deletion Confirmation</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
        <p>
          We're confirming that your account with scheduleflow has been
          successfully deleted as requested.
        </p>

        <div class="info-box">
          <h2>What This Means</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>
              Your personal information has been removed from our active systems
            </li>
            <li>Your login credentials will no longer work</li>
            <li>Any subscriptions or recurring payments have been canceled</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <p>
          We'd appreciate it if you could take a moment to let us know why you
          chose to leave:
        </p>
        <p style="text-align: center">
          <a href="{{feedbackLink}}" class="button">Share Your Feedback</a>
        </p>

        <p>
          If you believe this was done in error or if you have any questions,
          please contact our support team at support@scheduleflow.io within the
          next 3 days, as we may be able to restore your account.
        </p>

        <p>
          Best regards,<br />
          The Scheduleflow Team
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          This email was sent to {{email}} regarding your account with
          {{siteName}}.
        </p>
        <p>Â© {{currentYear}} {{companyName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>
          <a href="{{privacyPolicyLink}}">Privacy Policy</a> |
          <a href="{{termsOfServiceLink}}">Terms of Service</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
